## Summary
The Taxonomy API allows Enterprise users to programmatically manage their event schema in Amplitude, including creating, retrieving, updating, and deleting categories, event types, event properties, user properties, and group properties. The API uses HTTP Basic authentication and has concurrent and rate limits based on a cost model.

